    {
      "id": "detailed_1_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is in absolute mint condition, truly a showroom-quality specimen that has been meticulously maintained. The exterior paint is flawless with a deep, mirror-like finish, and the interior retains its original factory freshness with no signs of wear. All mechanical systems have been regularly serviced, ensuring the car performs exactly as it did the day it left the dealership. This is a rare find for a discerning buyer looking for a vehicle in near-perfect state.",
