      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "This meticulously maintained vehicle represents a premier opportunity for the discerning driver. Demonstrating consistent mechanical integrity and a well-preserved exterior, it offers a refined driving experience that balances performance with enduring value. A distinguished selection for those who prioritize reliability and sophisticated engineering in their next automotive investment.",
      "price": 34500.0,
