    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m looking to find a new home for my trusty car. It\u2019s been such a reliable ride and is still in really solid shape\u2014it's clearly been well-loved and looked after! It drives beautifully and is perfect for someone who wants a dependable vehicle that still looks great on the road. I've had some amazing memories in this car, and I'm sure you will too. Feel free to reach out if you want to come by and take it for a spin!",
      "price": 32500.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 37
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Up for sale is a driver-focused 2004 BMW M3 (E46) featuring the legendary S54B32 power plant. This high-revving 3.2L inline-six utilizes individual throttle bodies and dual-VANOS to deliver a linear power band up to its 8,000 RPM redline. Power is sent through a crisp Getrag 6-speed manual gearbox to the rear wheels via a variable M-Differential lock. Mechanically sound, the chassis has undergone critical rear subframe reinforcement and the VANOS system has been professionally serviced. Suspension remains tight with refreshed bushings and Bilstein dampers, ensuring the precise turn-in and mid-corner stability these cars are known for. While showing minor cosmetic patina consistent with spirited use, the mechanical integrity remains the priority. Recent fluid analysis confirms excellent engine health. A true analog machine for the discerning pilot.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.3,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 37
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_3_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_3",
      "description": "Used vehicle. Good condition. Well-maintained. Clean title. Ready for immediate pickup.",
      "price": 29500.0,
      "reputation": 0.4,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 37
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Offered for sale is a beautifully maintained 2017 BMW M2 finished in iconic Long Beach Blue Metallic over a Black Dakota leather interior. This car has been treated with care and driven responsibly. The exterior presents very well with a high-gloss finish; however, in the interest of full transparency, there are a few minor stone chips on the hood and a small scuff on the rear passenger-side wheel rim. The interior is smoke-free and remains crisp, with the blue contrast stitching still vibrant and the carbon fiber trim free of scratches. The engine pulls strongly through the entire rev range, and the dual-clutch transmission shifts seamlessly. I have kept a comprehensive binder of all service records, including a recent brake fluid flush and a fresh oil change performed less than 500 miles ago. The tires are in great shape with plenty of life left for the season. This is a turn-key performance coupe that balances daily usability with track-ready pedigree. Includes two keys and all original manuals.",
      "price": 32500.0,
      "reputation": 0.4,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 37
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_5_listing_5",
      "firm_id": "sybil_5",
      "description": "We are pleased to present this meticulously maintained vehicle, offering a superior balance of performance and sophistication. This specimen exhibits consistent mechanical care and a well-preserved interior, ensuring a refined driving experience. Engineered for reliability and presented in impressive aesthetic form, it represents an exceptional opportunity for the discerning driver seeking quality and longevity. Fully inspected and road-ready for immediate acquisition.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 37
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m looking to find a new home for my trusty car. It\u2019s been such a reliable ride for me and is still in really great shape, ready to hit the road with its next owner! It\u2019s been well-loved and drives like a dream. Whether you need a dependable daily driver or something for your next road trip, this one is a fantastic choice. Feel free to reach out if you have any questions!",
      "price": 32500.0,
